<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>188</hymn_number>
<key>Bb</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Nitlannak ah kan kal, dawh in a cer chin, Zing van sen le zan dapti
 lakah kan kal, Fek te-in hmailei nifatin in kan kal, Lam thluangthluan
 Jesuh zul tuah.

[C1]
   Zul tuah, Jesuh kha kan zulh lai, Zul tuah, Nifate zul tuah, Hmai ah
   a kan hruainak kip ah, Lam thluangthluan Jesuh cu kan zul lai.

[V2]
 A ceu bik nitlang le a muibik zantim, Hring dildel tlim-no le thal
 vulvau par caan, Zei caan paoh ah Jesuh fialmi cu zul tuah, Lam
 thluangthluan Jesuh zul tuah.

[C2]
   Zul tuah, Jesuh kha kan zulh lai, Zul tuah, Nifate zul tuah, Hmai ah
   a kan hruainak kip ah, Lam thluangthluan Jesuh cu kan zul lai.

[V3]
 Aa dawh bik nitlang le a muimi thladem, Thlichia to-tho hrang in
 hnabei dongh tikah, nitlak khuamuih zongah A-mah i bochan, Lam
 thluangthluan Jesuh zul tuah.

[C3]
   Zul tuah, Jesuh kha kan zulh lai, Zul tuah, Nifate zul tuah, Hmai ah
   a kan hruainak kip ah, Lam thluangthluan Jesuh cu kan zul lai.</lyrics>
<title>NITLANNAK AH KAN KAL CH188</title>
</song>